<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About QuickShop</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Your additional CSS styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: url('https://source.unsplash.com/1600x900/?electronics') no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .about-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 30px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #007bff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      text-align: justify;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: #007bff;
    }

    .about-content ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .about-content ul li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-info a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .contact-info a:hover {
      color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <h1>About QuickShop</h1>
      <p>
        QuickShop is a web application designed to help users compare
        prices of various products. It allows you to search for products, apply
        filters, and view detailed information about different items to make
        informed purchase decisions.
      </p>

      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Search for a wide range of products.</li>
        <li>Apply filters to narrow down your choices.</li>
        <li>View product details and prices for easy comparison.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or feedback, please feel free to contact us at
          <a href="mailto:info@quickshop.com">info@quickshop.com</a>.
          <p style="text-align: center;"><a href='/home' style="color: blue; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">Go to Home page</a></p>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
